{"tid":2163931,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［天下極權一樣黑］白羅斯警暴片要打國際戰線","createTime":"2020-08-19T02:57:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-19T03:33:54.000Z","uid":93793,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"afa5a659d3fc87a9004f208c204505a4b89b4c74","tid":2163931,"uid":93793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T02:57:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/franakviacorka/status/1295765187656585216?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffranakviacorka%2Fstatus%2F1295765187656585216%3Fs%3D21&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5pnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=1c5a0bd0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffranakviacorka%2Fstatus%2F1295765187656585216%3Fs%3D21&h=97c0775d\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/franakviacorka/status/1295765187656585216?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n示威之初（9號到14號）警暴造成傷痕<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CEBoio1gFnG/?igshid=ynwb5n73ym8i\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCEBoio1gFnG%2F%3Figshid%3Dynwb5n73ym8i&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5pnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=16c19d43\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCEBoio1gFnG%2F%3Figshid%3Dynwb5n73ym8i&h=a2935043\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CEBoio1gFnG/?igshid=ynwb5n73ym8i</a><br />\n<br />\n同場加映：記者（同平民）喺街到俾人綁去軍營毒打<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n白羅斯箇然有好多令人好感動嘅消息：<br />\n<br />\n主要工廠工人罷工、<br />\n<br />\n國立劇院總監表態俾炒，全部artist總辭、<br />\n<br />\nIT界300 CEO威脅移民、<br />\n<br />\n奧運代表嘅運動員表態罷賽、<br />\n<br />\n國立電視台員工罷工兼播員工嗌口號<br />\n<br />\n但即使佢哋大多數咁團結，佢哋一樣面對一個極無恥嘅極權，而佢哋受到嘅壓逼一樣一路無停過，而佢哋政府開始出埋暗招喺街到綁架人、派人去街頭搞分化、廠佬開始勸工人停止罷工<br />\n<br />\n我哋可唔可以話俾白羅斯人聽，喺對抗極權嘅路上佢哋唔孤單？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外一齊打twitter戰線：TG@TwitterHelpBot"},{"pid":"e1105099b858aa2fa28d718a9239119a79ee8e93","tid":2163931,"uid":93793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T03:17:06.000Z","msg":"分化手段<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hannaliubakova/status/1295701060527546368?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhannaliubakova%2Fstatus%2F1295701060527546368%3Fs%3D21&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5pnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=97c66c2b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhannaliubakova%2Fstatus%2F1295701060527546368%3Fs%3D21&h=0636fc53\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hannaliubakova/status/1295701060527546368?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n派車遊街，喺街到大聲播口號<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/franakviacorka/status/1295856451257344007?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffranakviacorka%2Fstatus%2F1295856451257344007%3Fs%3D21&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5pnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=47fde8ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffranakviacorka%2Fstatus%2F1295856451257344007%3Fs%3D21&h=2280fb6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/franakviacorka/status/1295856451257344007?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n喺街邊搞小動作，話示威者唔係吸毒就賣淫<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/franakviacorka/status/1295617912124911616?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffranakviacorka%2Fstatus%2F1295617912124911616%3Fs%3D21&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5pnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=716677dc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffranakviacorka%2Fstatus%2F1295617912124911616%3Fs%3D21&h=419e6eab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/franakviacorka/status/1295617912124911616?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n因為人民籌咗錢俾劈炮嘅警察軍人，所以馬上開張表揚名單穩定軍心<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/franakviacorka/status/1295704228250497024?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffranakviacorka%2Fstatus%2F1295704228250497024%3Fs%3D21&d=%2BN%2BzEUDrQz9IsHzLxo0c5pnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=5b52c17f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ffranakviacorka%2Fstatus%2F1295704228250497024%3Fs%3D21&h=3ed52380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/franakviacorka/status/1295704228250497024?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n失蹤人口<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後完得輕鬆啲：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KHNQANK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKHNQANK.jpg&h=cf0c36b8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「嗰個人（獨裁總理）而家唯一可以搞嘅公投係：<br />\n<br />\nA.佢會搭火車走<br />\nB.佢會搭飛機走<br />\nC.佢會坐其他嘢走<br />\n<br />\n唔係嘅話都可以叫佢收皮。」"},{"pid":"54915f169bc0ef6ca5a81f9e2753627c282fd85f","tid":2163931,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T03:28:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbc071ad1fd02bfd77444ef2816fe57a220c1e08","tid":2163931,"uid":223428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T03:33:54.000Z","msg":"Retweet!"}]}